{"content":"<li class=\"n-box-item date-title\" data-end=\"1414990799\" data-start=\"1414900800\" data-txt=\"Saturday, December 21, 2019\">Sunday, November  2, 2014</li><li class=\"n-box-item sa-box-item\" data-id=\"2084025\" data-ts=\"1414971219\"><div class=\"media media-overflow-fix\"><div class=\"media-left\"><a class=\"box-ticker\" href=\"/symbol/SAPE\" target=\"_blank\">SAPE</a></div><div class=\"media-body\"><h4 class=\"media-heading\"><a href=\"/news/2084025-publicis-in-talks-to-acquire-sapient-wsj\" sasource=\"on_the_move_news_fidelity\" target=\"_blank\">Publicis in talks to acquire Sapient - WSJ</a></h4><ul><li> A deal to buy Sapient (NASDAQ:<a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SAPE' title='Sapient Corporation'>SAPE</a>) <a href=\"http://online.wsj.com/articles/publicis-in-talks-to-acquire-sapient-sources-1414959578\" target=\"_blank\">could be announced</a> as soon as Monday.</li><li>Publicis' (<a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBCBF' title='Publicis S.A.'>OTCPK:PBCBF</a>, <a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PGPEF' title='Publicis Groupe S.A.'>OTCQX:PGPEF</a>, <a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PUBGY' title='Publicis Groupe S.A. ADR'>OTCQX:PUBGY</a>) planned merger with Omnicom (NYSE:<a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OMC' title='Omnicom Group Inc.'>OMC</a>) fell apart in May, and its sales growth  has slowed recent quarters.</li><li>With Sapient, Publicis would add a more digital-focus to its traditional creative business. CEO&nbsp;Maurice Levy <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/media/2014/jul/09/publicis-omnicom-merger-maurice-levy\" target=\"_blank\">has said</a> he wants Publicis to more closely resemble \"an internet company.\"</li><li>SAPE's market cap is $2.5B; its revenue was $1.26B last year.</li></ul><div class=\"tiny-share-widget\" data-id=\"2084025\" data-linked=\"Publicis in talks to acquire Sapient - WSJ\" data-tweet=\"$SAPE $SAPE $PBCBF - Publicis in talks to acquire Sapient - WSJ https://seekingalpha.com/news/2084025-publicis-in-talks-to-acquire-sapient-wsj?source=tweet\" data-url=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/2084025-publicis-in-talks-to-acquire-sapient-wsj\"><div class=\"icon share-btn c-email\" title=\"Email a friend\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-twitter\" title=\"Share on Twitter\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-facebook\" title=\"Share on Facebook\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-linkedin\" title=\"Share on Linkedin\">&nbsp;</div></div><span class=\"mc_gray_separator\">|</span>  6:33 PM <span class='mc_gray_separator'>|</span> <span class='comments-n'><span class='comments-container '>2&nbsp;<span class='comments-number'>Comments</span></span></span></div></div></li>","count":1,"message":null,"success":true,"today":{"start":1576904400,"end":1576990799,"str":"Saturday, December 21, 2019"},"yesterday":{"start":1576818000,"end":1576904399}}